    <div>
      <header>
        <marquee class="text-xl bg-slate-900 text-slate-50 font-serif">Selamat datang di Devtech Hidayah</marquee>
        <div class="p-5">
          <h1 class="text-3xl protest-guerrilla-regular">Devtech Hidayah</h1>
          <h2 class="text-xl">Mari dengan membaca artikel semakin banyak ilmu yang di dapat</h2>
        </div>
      </header>
      <nav id="nav" class="bg-gray-400 backdrop-filter sticky top-0">
        <div class="navbar flex items-center justify-between p-2">
          <div class="logo">
            <figure class="border-2 p-2">
              <img src="assets/images/Devtech hidayah.png" alt="" width="50px" loading="lazy" class="lg:w-20 h-20" />
            </figure>
          </div>
          <ul class="list lg:flex md:flex sm:flex gap-2 justify-center font-bold p-3 text-xl lexend-uniquifier hidden">
            <li><a href="/">HOME</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">ABOUT</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blogs">BLOG</a></li>
            <li><a href="">CONTACT</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <main id="main" class="my-10 w-full">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap items-center">
          <h1 class="text-3xl text-center font-bold">About</h1>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-10 flex-wrap p-5">
            <figure class="border-2 p-2">
              <img src="/assets/images/user.png" alt="my-image" width="300px" />
            </figure>
            <article class="lg:w-1/2 w-full flex flex-col p-5">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Apriyanto Ulami S</h2>
              <p class="mt-2 text-justify">
                Hello! I'm Apriyanto Ulami S, the author behind this blog. With over 10 years of experience in technology and lifestyle writing, I'm passionate about sharing insights, tips, and stories that inspire and inform.
                <br />
                <br />
                My goal with this blog is to create a space where readers can find valuable information on a wide range of topics, from the latest tech trends to practical lifestyle advice.
                <br />
                <br />
                I believe in the power of knowledge and the importance of continuous learning. When I'm not writing, you can find me exploring new hiking trails, experimenting with new recipes in the kitchen, or tinkering with the latest
                gadgets.
              </p>
            </article>
            <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-5 border-2">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Blog Mission</h2>
              <p class="mt-5 text-center w-1/2">
                My mission is to provide high-quality, engaging content that helps readers navigate the complexities of modern life, embrace new technologies, and find balance in their personal and professional lives.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">Connect With Me</h2>
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center mt-5">
              <ul class="flex gap-5">
                <li> 
                  <figure class="border-2 p-2">
                    <img src="/assets/images/github.png" alt="github" width="30px">
                  </figure>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <figure class="border-2 p-2">
                    <img src="/assets/images/instagram.png" alt="instagram" width="30px">
                  </figure> 
                </li>
                <li>
                  <figure class="border-2 p-2">
                    <img src="/assets/images/linkedin.png" alt="linkedin" width="30px">
                  </figure>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <figure class="border-2 p-2">
                    <img src="/assets/images/email.png" alt="email" width="30px">
                  </figure>
                </li>
